These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, april
There 2 different types of food: lime, pomegranate
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, aristoff
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Birthday      | march  | april   |
| Food   | pomegranate     | lime   |
| Pet         | hedgehog | chinchilla |
| Cigar     | pall-mall | aristoff    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, montecristo
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, parkour
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk
House: cape-cod, palace
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the palace house##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Cigar          | bongani     | montecristo |
| Sport   | parkour | sailing  |
| Beverage           | almond-milk         | milk     |
| House     | cape-cod   | palace    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, baseball
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, montecristo
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Flower    | lily     | poppy |
| Sport         | baseball | handball    |
| Cigar         | blend         | montecristo        |
| Hobby   | collecting         | rock-climbing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
