The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, september
1. the modern house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality      | french     | colombian |
| Game          | billiard   | whist  |
| House         | ranch-style | modern     |
| Birthday   | july  | september         |

