.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, green
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy
House: victorian, modern
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, cabbage
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
3. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Color    | brown | green    |
| Flower         | daisy        | balloon-flower |
| House         | victorian          | modern     |
| Food   | eggplant        | cabbage     |

 